1
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:35,560
The time has come.

2
00:00:37,120 --> 00:00:37,650
Execute!

3
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:42,490
Stop the execution!

4
00:00:58,960 --> 00:00:59,880
Yun!

5
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:02,460
Mo Di had been sending people to spy on me.

6
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:04,720
So I had to wait until the last moment.

7
00:01:04,720 --> 00:01:05,840
Yu.

8
00:01:10,800 --> 00:01:12,840
I actually knew all about your choice.

9
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:15,200
I won't let you die for nothing.

10
00:01:20,600 --> 00:01:23,520
Yu, falling in love with you in this life

11
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:25,840
is my greatest blessing.

12
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:43,640
Jiuyun.

13
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:46,640
Sorry.

14
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:48,560
I only found this.

15
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:39,960
Moyu, it's not that easy to escape.

16
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:43,160
I've been guarding against your betrayal.

17
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:47,400
I will take you down when you are helpless and isolated.

18
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:50,000
Su Cheng is your own grandson.

19
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:52,120
Why did you try to kill him?

20
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,780
He's not my real grandfather.

21
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:59,170
He just values my identity as a remnant of the previous dynasty.

22
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:02,160
Although we are not related by blood,

23
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:05,200
your mother was my adopted daughter.

24
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:06,720
Without me,

25
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:09,440
what resources would you have to restore the country?

26
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:12,040
If you had submitted to me earlier,

27
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:14,400
you wouldn't be in this situation today.

28
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:16,960
Didn't I endure hardships to get all of this?

29
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:20,280
You just wanted to use me to annex Great Jin.

30
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:21,960
But in fact,

31
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,840
I was almost used by you.

32
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:26,880
You used my resources to become the God of War,

33
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:28,160
monopolized power,

34
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:31,120
and wanted to use the shadow I gave you

35
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:33,160
to seek financial power.

36
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:36,370
Didn't you just want to completely escape my control

37
00:03:36,480 --> 00:03:37,600
and betray me?

38
00:03:40,160 --> 00:03:43,200
These two men are terribly scheming.

39
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:44,800
But

40
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:47,320
you still couldn't fool me.

41
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:49,120
Do you know why?

42
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:52,120
Because you have a fatal weakness.

43
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,760
This woman.

44
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:58,280
I could never figure out

45
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:01,600
where you hid the Elixir Manual.

46
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:04,160
Later, I found that you planted a yellow flower tree

47
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,880
in the God of War's mansion,

48
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:08,320
and often went there to sacrifice.

49
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:11,240
Only then did I understand.

50
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,200
It seems

51
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:16,440
you gave the Elixir Manual to this woman.

52
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:22,600
But you are destined to fail.

53
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:23,720
Because

54
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:26,960
from the moment you saved this woman,

55
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:31,760
your every move has been under my control.

56
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:35,320
And you,

57
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:39,280
thinking you could reverse the situation by knowing my plan.

58
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:43,200
Unfortunately, you are just as stupid as him.

59
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:45,090
Overestimating yourself.

60
00:04:49,159 --> 00:04:50,480
That's right.

61
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:53,920
I poisoned the whole river.

62
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:57,560
How do you have elixirs?

63
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,080
He is an alchemist,

64
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:01,460
so naturally, he can refine elixirs.

65
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,820
This is the Powerless Elixir he refined.

66
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,360
Jiuyun.

67
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,240
Yun,

68
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:14,880
don't!

69
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:16,740
Don't you want the Elixir Manual?

70
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:19,080
Let them go,

71
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,850
and I'll go with you.

72
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:27,880
Okay.

73
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:38,520
I have let them go.

74
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:40,680
Now write down the Pill Manual for me.

75
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,760
I can come back with you,

76
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:45,880
but there's no way I'll write down the Pill Manual.

77
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:48,640
Don't do things the hard way.

78
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:50,480
If I write down the Pill Manual now,

79
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:52,480
I probably won't live to see tomorrow,

80
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:54,200
let alone save the two of them.

81
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:57,600
But I am still a person of my word.

82
00:05:57,600 --> 00:06:00,080
As long as you promise to let the three of us go,

83
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:03,520
I can help you refine all the pills in the Pill Manual.

84
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:10,160
With the pill, we can figure out the complete formula.

85
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:12,560
Okay.

86
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:28,960
You wish you could memorize the ingredients.

87
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,840
This is a pill to enhance hearing.

88
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:39,440
This can enhance hearing?

89
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:41,100
Try it if you don't believe me.

90
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:48,920
Why don't you test its effects for me?

91
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,720
Modilikala.

92
00:07:12,080 --> 00:07:13,640
Monilikala.

93
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:16,800
Are you speaking a foreign language to your subordinate?

94
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,960
That's right.

95
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:20,480
It seems this pill is effective.

96
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:25,050
We will continue tomorrow.

97
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:14,640
Bo Baorui

98
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:15,170
Bo Baorui

99
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:18,980
Zhong Xia Qiang

100
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,140
Peng Yin

101
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,220
Kun Quan Xuhang

102
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:23,580
Quan Yulong

103
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,040
Licheng Lefei

104
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:27,120
Yunlong Yinyujia Guangjing

105
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,120
Luo Xiaocong Lin Xunbo
